#content
  %h1 Me robaron 
  %h2 Y ahora que hago? 
  %p El 60% de las personas no realizan la denuncia policial, ayudanos entre todos a cambiar esto y hacer nuestra ciudad un lugar mas seguro.
  %form{method:"POST",targer:"/submissions"}
    #when-where-wrapper.question-wrapper.hero-unit
      %h2 
        <i class="icon-map-marker"></i>
        Ubicacion y Tiempo
      .question-content.row-fluid
        .left.span7
          #map-field.map-container.well
            %div#map-wrapper{ style: "height:100%;width:100%;" }
            %div.fields
              %input#lat{ type: "hidden",  name: "submission[lat]" }
              %input#long{ type: "hidden", name: "submission[long]" }
              %input#seccionalNumber{ type: "hidden", name: "submission[station_number]" }

        .right.span5
          %h2 Cuando?
          %input.ui-datepicker.well{name: "happened_at"}

      :javascript
        $(function(){
            $("#map-field").mapWidget();

            $('.ui-datepicker').datetimepicker({
              dateFormat: "yy-mm-dd",
            });
        });
      
    - questions.each do |question|
      = haml :'helpers/_question', locals: { question: question }, layout: false
      
    %input.btn.btn-danger{type: "submit", value: "Denunciar"}
